  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这款3D赛车游戏设计一个清晰的架构图。核心模块是Game，它应该作为整个系统的入口。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Main"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那Main和Game之间的关系是怎样的？Main是启动入口，然后调用Game吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Main启动后直接关联到Game。Game模块负责协调所有子系统。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Main",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把Main和Game的连接画好了。接下来Game需要渲染3D场景吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是的，Game会驱动ThreeScene进行渲染，这个关系标注为\"Renderiza\"。同时Game还要导入赛道和赛车资源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Car和Track都是从Game导入的？那它们和ThreeScene的关系呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Car",
        "Track",
        "ThreeScene"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Car和Track被Game导入后，会交给ThreeScene来实际渲染。所以ThreeScene要同时连接Car和Track。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ThreeScene",
        "Car",
        "Track"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加。现在Game还需要接入哪些子系统？物理引擎和输入控制应该少不了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Physics",
        "Controls"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，Physics物理引擎、Controls输入控制，还有Camera相机系统，这三个都用Hook方式接入Game，表示它们是事件回调机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Game",
        "Physics",
        "Controls",
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Hook标注已加上。Camera也是Hook方式？它不是渲染相关的吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Camera"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Camera虽然和渲染有关，但这里指的是相机控制逻辑，比如跟随赛车、切换视角，所以也是通过Hook注册到Game的更新循环中。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Camera",
        "Game"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了。那未来规划呢？有没有扩展模块？",
